m) of the current IACT, MAGIC is the best candidate to reach a\nlow energy threshold in these peculiar conditions. Here we discuss the\nfeasibility of such observations.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 6 Jul 2009 16:10:28 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-08-13"}
