ent at the layer where Ne viii is formed in the quiet\nSun, and that the magnetic structures expand more strongly in the dark part\nthan in the bright part of this quiet Sun region.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 6 Jul 2009 19:05:51 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-07-17"}
